      <div class="msgContentFrame">Some of my funny ideas (one for each class :D) (don't want to participate for the prices, just like the idea of designing skills and sharing them :D) <br /> <br /><u><b>Warrior-Skill:</b></u> <br /> <br /><b>Name: Backfire</b> <br />Skilltype: Rifle-Attack <br />Description: Your shoot backfires, leaving behind a dust cloud which blinds all near enemy's for 5 Seconds. You suffer from the condition blackout for 3 seconds). (35sec recast) <br /> <br /> <br /><u><b>Elementalist-Skill:</b></u> <br /> <br /><b>Name: Vapor Blade</b> <br />Skilltype: Elite-Enchantment <br />Description: Your dagger-attacks ignore armor-rating (10seconds). When this enchantment ends, you and adjacent foes are blinded for 5 seconds. (30sec recast) <br /> <br /> <br /><u><b>Ranger-Skill:</b></u> <br /> <br /><b>Name: &quot;Freestyle Fighting!&quot;</b> <br />Skilltype: Melee-Bowattack <br />Description: You swing your bow around you. Attacking foes hit suffer from vulnerability for 3 seconds and get knocked down. (30sec recast) <br /> <br /> <br /><u><b>Necromancer-Skill:</b></u> <br /> <br /><b>Name: Mark of Insanity</b> <br />Skilltype: Mark <br />Description: Places a Mark of Insanity, which inflicts burning and frozen condition to attacking foes and foes, activating skills. (8 sec duration, 33sec recast) <br /> <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Nov 17th 2010  8:05pm by CitrusO2 </span></i> <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Nov 17th 2010  8:22pm by CitrusO2 </span></i></div>
