      <div class="msgContentFrame">Skill Name: <b>Comfortably Numb</b>  <br /> <br />Conceived as a mesmer skill, could be worked to necromancer or &quot;Blue Mace Lady&quot;. <br /> <br />Basic Description: Your enemy/hostile target's skills take longer to recharge (be it a percentage or flat number of seconds). In addition, your target takes a 20% (adjustable) less damage from physical and elemental damage and moves 20% slower while the effect lasts.  <br /> <br />If cast on allies, does not cause the skill recharge penalty (damage reduction and speed decrease persist).  <br /> <br />It's hard to add numbers without having any idea as far as balancing et.al., but that's the gist of it. :)</div>
